    "Humans dominate AI, but AI is beginning to manage larger and more complex work areas.",
    "AI is used to automate selected parts of manual and repetitive tasks such as code generation, documentation, testing, and deployment.",
    "AI is also used to assist humans in tasks such as design, troubleshooting, and decision-making Formulation: S2: P 2 {A(H 1) → {B(AI 3-4 or H 2-3) → {C(T 1-2), D(H 2-3 or AI 3-4)}}} Scenario 3: AI assumes role(s).",
